content: daizhengxue: Made significant contributions by merging 4 PRs, including a major feature addition for DeepSeek AI provider support (#2067, +96k/-44k lines) and fixing related bugs in the DeepSeek API (#2186, +28k/-17k lines). Created and subsequently closed 2 issues related to database connections and data provider refactoring (#2158, #2126). Activity was concentrated on a few days with a balanced focus between feature development, bug fixes, and other work, primarily modifying code files with substantial line changes (+17k/-17k lines).
